{"tid":1800282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尖沙咀警署811事件33人被捕 29人被控暴動 4人無條件釋放","createTime":"2019-12-27T15:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T16:36:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58f95044884dfa960e3427cdc00b0a031049020e","tid":1800282,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"8月11號尖沙咀警署外有人堵路, 並向警署投擲汽油彈, 以及向警員投擲硬物.<br />\n        警方說, 被捕的33人中, 29人已合共被控以一項暴動罪, 他們包括23男6女, 年齡介乎15至41歲. 其中4名男子各被控以一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪, 一名男子就被控以一項無牌管有槍械或彈藥罪. 案件明年2月24日在西九龍裁判法院再提堂.<br />\n        而警方經諮詢法律意見後, 同案另外4名被捕人士已獲無條件釋放.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20191227212648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20191227212648&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=432ca9bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20191227212648</a>"},{"pid":"9fb587ef8fa5cf81e1af62a27e44999277501c30","tid":1800282,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9828e9e7619e915eb005353360acea8fccec3e3","tid":1800282,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"清算檢察官"},{"pid":"10b514861beb23a1fd988b1d402f5c3d8a938015","tid":1800282,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fb587ef8fa5cf81e1af62a27e44999277501c30","tid":1800282,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a